## Text Boxes (Frames)

```js
const { Paragraph, TextRun, FrameProperties, HorizontalPositionAlign, VerticalPositionAlign } = require('docx');

new Paragraph({
  text: 'This is in a text box',
  frame: {
    position: {
      x: 1000,
      y: 1000,
    },
    width: 4000,
    height: 2000,
    anchor: {
      horizontal: FrameAnchorType.MARGIN,
      vertical: FrameAnchorType.MARGIN,
    },
  },
})
```

